About


We are full service agents and will assist our clients in buying or selling their home or help with a new construction project. In addition, we also offer property management and Home Watch services. We will help property owners in a tenant placement process for self - management or provide full property management services. This would include advertising the property, screening a prospective tenant, providing the lease and managing the property for the duration of the lease. Our Home Watch service will provide peace of mind to residential and second home owners in our area who spend extended time away from Florida. Our clients come first and we are always just a phone call away. We take great pride in our customer service and will do our very best to exceed your expectations.
